-- Eskom Gets Strike Notice From South Africa's National Union of Mineworkers
-- Nicky Smith
-- 2010-07-01T05:23:53Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-01/eskom-gets-strike-notice-from-south-africa-s-national-union-of-mineworkers.html

          
          
             The National Union of Mineworkers
plans to serve a strike notice to Eskom Holdings Ltd. today,
said Lesiba Seshoka, a spokesman for the labor union.  
 “If they have not been served already they will be served
this morning,” Seshoka said in a phone interview today from
Johannesburg.  
